 and\nit does not have a tidal origin. The interaction between the two could have\ntriggered the star formation in NGC 4656UV and increased the star formation in\nthe northeast side of NGC 4656.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 16:40:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
