ion of perturbations\nwhich can be distinguished from Quintessence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 18:02:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 15:39:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
