rial length scales and\nenables the development of parameterized microstructural database for material\ndesign and manufacturing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 19:14:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Sep 2018 18:50:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 13:41:24 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 15:57:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-04"}
